data.description: Located east of I-95 in Oakland Park's Central Business District. This sweet 2/1 in North Andrews Gardens is ready for a new owner to love to its next level. Large and completely fenced yard w/ room for a pool or addition. Seller would consider a lease back for 30 days post-closing. Appliances include stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher, oven and washer/dryer. Interior laundry room. Florida room off kitchen could be nice home office. Covered carport. Screened front porch. Super close to the bustling Oakland Park "downtown". Easy access to downtown Ft Lauderdale and the beaches. Great central location. Check around, this is a great opportunity to own a home, with land, in a fabulous location. Seller requires 3 weeks post closing occupancy.
